OL,3,CReform UK's Hampshire mayoral
OL,4,Ccandidate Chris Parry suspended
OL,6,FReform UK has suspended its Hampshire
OL,7,Fmayoral candidate, Chris Parry,
OL,8,Ffollowing a series of controversial
OL,9,Fsocial media posts.
OL,11,FThe retired Royal Navy rear admiral
OL,12,Fappeared to liken a Jewish
OL,13,Fneighbourhood watch group to
OL,14,F"Islamists on horseback" following an
OL,15,Farson attack in north London.
OL,17,FIn January, he was forced to apologise
OL,18,Fafter an old Twitter post surfaced in
OL,19,Fwhich he suggested British-born
OL,20,Fcabinet minister David Lammy should
OL,21,F"go home" to the Caribbean.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@XO]}D@AOU}D@IO]
