OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774375557
OL,3,CReform UK's Hampshire mayoral
OL,4,Ccandidate Chris Parry suspended
OL,6,FDr Chris Parry was only announced in
OL,7,FDecember 2025 as Reform UK's candidate
OL,8,Fto be the first mayor of Hampshire and
OL,9,Fthe Solent. The inaugural election was
OL,10,Fsubsequently delayed by the government
OL,11,Ffrom 2026 until 2028.
OL,13,FA Reform UK spokesperson said: "Chris
OL,14,FParry has been suspended by Reform UK,
OL,15,Fpending investigation."
OL,17,FITV News Meridian understands that
OL,18,FChris Parry's mayoral candidacy has
OL,19,Falso been suspended. Chris Parry has
OL,20,Fbeen approached for comment.
OL,26,@uD@`OUwD@WO]
