OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774375557
OL,3,CReform UK's Hampshire mayoral
OL,4,Ccandidate Chris Parry suspended
OL,6,FThe Liberal Democrats said Mr Parry's
OL,7,Flatest remarks were "deeply
OL,8,Finsensitive, insulting and not
OL,9,Fbefitting of someone who wants to hold
OL,10,Fpublic office."
OL,12,FThe Conservative leader of Hampshire
OL,13,FCounty Council, Cllr Nick Adams-King,
OL,14,Fsaid: "Public office is a privilege,
OL,15,Fnot a platform for prejudice.
OL,26,@oD@UOUrD@OO]vD@GOU
