CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774375557
OL,3,CReform UK's Hampshire mayoral
OL,4,Ccandidate Chris Parry suspended
OL,6,F"I'm glad action has been taken, and I
OL,7,Fwill continue to champion a Hampshire
OL,8,Fwhere every resident, from every
OL,9,Fbackground, can live without fear and
OL,10,Fwith confidence in those who represent
OL,11,Fthem."
OL,13,FA Labour Party spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"Nigel Farage should have booted Chris
OL,15,FParry out of his party months ago.
OL,17,F"The fact he didn't shows what a weak
OL,18,Fleader he is and just how far he's
OL,19,Fwilling to drag politics into the
OL,20,Fgutter."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]vD@AOUyD@AOU|D@HO]
