PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1774375557
OL,3,CReform UK's Hampshire mayoral
OL,4,Ccandidate Chris Parry suspended
OL,6,FThe new mayoral position is due to get
OL,7,Fpowers from Westminster over areas
OL,8,Fsuch as transport, housing and skills.
OL,10,FThe mayoral combined authority will
OL,11,Fencompass the whole of the ceremonial
OL,12,Fcounty of Hampshire, including the
OL,13,Fcities of Portsmouth and Southampton.
OL,14,FIt will also include the Isle of Wight.
OL,16,FThe first election was planned for May
OL,17,F2026 but ministers announced in
OL,18,FDecember 2025 that they would delay
OL,19,Fthe poll until 2028.
